question: Where can I find restaurant in the direction of Brick + Mortar Design Studio, Easton, PA within 160 kilometers from Covered Bridge Park, Slatington, PA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-75.621665 40.747433)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-75.22574 40.697873)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-75.621665 40.747433)',4326)::geography, 160000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-75.621665 40.747433)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
